and the Lagrangian is 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathcal{L}=\sqrt{-\det\left(\eta_{\mu\nu}+\frac{1}{M_{\text{P1}}}h_{\mu\nu}\right)}\phi
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $M_{\text{P1}}=G_{N}^{-1/2}\approx10^{19}\GeV$
\end_inset

 is the Planck scale, 它的引入可以使
\begin_inset Formula $h_{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

具有质量
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

次方的量纲。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
类似地，
\begin_inset Formula $h_{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

的动能项为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathcal{L}=M_{\text{P1}}^{2}\sqrt{-\det\left(\eta_{\mu\nu}+\frac{1}{M_{\text{P1}}}h_{\mu\nu}\right)}R\left[\eta_{\mu\nu}+\frac{1}{M_{\text{P1}}}h_{\mu\nu}\right]
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

